&lt;img class="thumbnail" alt="Thumbnail" src="/images/3a4b2132cdefc03527223d707a6a5ce6bffc.jpeg" /&gt;</code></pre>

  <h2>Fluid images</h2>
  <section class="example">
    <img class="fluid" src="/images/b62a0a54fbed94d91e3d66328b783a811b47.jpeg" alt="Defoliation" />
